data.description: Beautifully updated home on just under an acre with a modern farmhouse feel! Features butcher-block countertops, large open living space, en suite primary bath and a huge recreational room upstairs. Three bedrooms downstairs with an extra room upstairs that can be used as an office or a fourth bedroom. The huge backyard is fenced in, with a deck, storage shed, garden space and chicken coop!
